                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Improving upper body strength is one of the most sought-after achievements in men and women lifters. The quality of upper body strength can drastically impact functionality in our daily lives. From carrying groceries to pushing doors open, we use upper body muscles like the triceps every day. </span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">This guide on the tricep dumbbell kickback provides information on how to execute the exercise and what muscles are used. It details the numerous benefits of this exercise, including improved upper body strength and increased bone density. Keep reading to learn more about the tricep dumbbell kickback and its benefits in this guide.</span></p>                    </div>
